title: Don't Let People Label You | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Don't Let People Label You | Joel Osteen
description:
If you're going to become everything that God created you to be, you have to remove the labels that are holding you back. People don't determine our destiny; God does.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
